yena rājayogenānekarājyabhogasamaya eva / anekapārthivavinoda\app{\lem[wit={P,N1,D1,U1}]{prekṣaṇasamaya}\rdg[wit={U2}]{prekṣyaṇasamaya}} eva / bahutarakālaṃ śarīrasthitirbhavati / sa \app{\lem[wit={P,N1,D1,U2}]{eva}\rdg[wit={U2}]{evaṃ}} rājayogaḥ / tasyaite bhedāḥ / 
